Legend:
 '+' = added feature
 '*' = bug fix
 '-' = removed feature

Version 0.07
============
Kean Pedersen:
  - Removed the 32x32 tiles, was too ugly/bit/unused

Aaron Kill (new developer):
  + Alert to notify when you don't have enough money to build an item
  + Alert to notify when you have 1000 or less credits
  + Alert to notify when you have 0 credits
  + Speed control
  + Population display
  + Taxes paid each month
